page.title: 01LAND COVERAGE
page.content: Our area is mostly compiled of fields which mainly belong to the farms.The height of the ground of our area is about seven an a half metres above sea-level.The next largest area is covered by orchards.Houses cover quite a bit of land but do not appear in all the small squares.Roads and tracks cover a smaller percentage of land.The smallest area of land is covered by drains which drain the water from the land because it is so low.The grid is a 4 by 3 grid.In each grid there are a hundred small squares.On page 2 it will show you how many percent all the items are in each grid.
